platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Marvel Unlimiteds tagline is Never stop reading comics. And given the sheer amount of content in there, thats entirely possible. Its pretty tough to overstate the amount of content in Marvel Unlimited. New titles turn up every week, sometimes as soon as six months after they hit stores. That means fresh issues of Asgardians of the Galaxy, Runaways, and Immortal Hulk.
New titles turn up every week, sometimes as soon as six months after they hit stores. That means fresh issues of the hottest comics at your fingertips.
De nouvelles BD apparaissent chaque semaine, parfois seulement six mois aprs leur parution en librairie. Vous trouverez donc les numros les plus en vogue juste  porte de doigts.
